Package: MIRA
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2016-09-12
Title: Methylation-based inference of regulatory activity
Description: measures the degree of "dip" in methylation
    level surrounding a regulatory site of interest, such as a 
    transcription factor binding sites.
Author: Nathan Sheffield <http://www.databio.org> [aut, cre],
    Christoph Bock [cre],
    John Lawson [aut]
Maintainer: Nathan Sheffield <nathan@code.databio.org>
